data.description: 3 Bedroom on corner lot with detached garage. 37 Braun Street in Glouster is a wonderful family home with space, character, a detached garage, and more for under $140,000! The shaded covered porch expands the entire back and side portion of the home, and provides access to the backyard. There is off street parking, as well as parking next to the home and garage.
